{"tid":1736253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攻唔入係因為成班人豬咀都冇就話衝","createTime":"2019-11-18T17:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T02:14:45.000Z","uid":123302,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6db12310b1e918b0a49c0e233050fb8747b02b","tid":1736253,"uid":123302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"其實中大已經係咁<br />\n<br />\n出左嚟5個月 我真係睇唔撚明點解咁撚多人仲可以冇豬咀 <br />\n<br />\n5金鋪一撚早返晒貨 6系都齊貨<br />\n<br />\n你班友就係都要戴口罩上場<br />\n<br />\n點撚樣攻啊 一個tg就收你皮啦<br />\n<br />\n企前線 得口罩 然後一有tg就跑走 然後跑唔得遠就洗面 大佬tg都未撚散你咁近洗乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n企中場 得口罩 然後就大大聲屌d有豬咀既話有gear做乜唔企前 喂一隊滅火隊梗撚係前中後分散企啦 你估tg唔會射落後場??<br />\n<br />\n仲有D口罩既真係可以恃住自己冇gear 話你有gear驚乜春野 人地開tg我咪唔撚驚囉 人地開布袋開橡膠 點硬食啊?????<br />\n<br />\n識得出嚟話救手足 GEAR呢屌你????? 冇gear仲要係咁講呢D說話玩分化 不如你地自己買返個豬咀泳鏡先啦好嗎???"},{"pid":"aceb34985fd96b5d443e3c725853974d0c42c0a7","tid":1736253,"uid":123302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"32aadf0c494cd90ca037edf4052963ef9c87f123","tid":1736253,"uid":123302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"c45fcebc6ecafd15e230352755ed85d494345e78","tid":1736253,"uid":26687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"唔識教到佢識"},{"pid":"ad9287ff09754a3be2134b805025c4231145d9d2","tid":1736253,"uid":123302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"4f5c94596b05bc49882025f9dbf509bdeb9d234f","tid":1736253,"uid":123302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:26:19.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"42cc93015aaa1cb4904b527e202400d23cd31a07","tid":1736253,"uid":14377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"有部分和理非啱啱先升做勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces